"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Gunmen opened fire at Crocus City Concert hall near Moscow in 2024, killing 149 and injuring more than 500.\",            \"english_title\": \"Shooting at Concert Hall\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hombres armados dispararon en el Crocus City Concert Hall cerca de Mosc\u00fa en 2024, matando a 149 e hiriendo a m\u00e1s de 500.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tiroteo en Sala de Conciertos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ren\u00e9 Redzepi had previously apologised after ex-employees of the Danish restaurant accused him of creating a toxic work environment.\",            \"english_title\": \"Chef Apologizes for Toxic Workplace\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ren\u00e9 Redzepi se disculp\u00f3 despu\u00e9s de que ex-empleados del restaurante dan\u00e9s lo acusaron de crear un ambiente de trabajo t\u00f3xico.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Chef se Disculpa por Ambiente T\u00f3xico\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Rastriya Swatatantra Party has won a large majority in an election dominated by issues including corruption.\",            \"english_title\": \"Party Wins Election\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Partido Rastriya Swatatantra gan\u00f3 una gran mayor\u00eda en una elecci\u00f3n dominada por problemas como la corrupci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Partido Gana Elecci\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Modelling agent used businesses to recruit girls and arrange US visas to visit Jeffrey Epstein, Brazilian women tell BBC.\",            \"english_title\": \"Agent Recruits Girls\",            \"translated_version\": \"Agente de modelos us\u00f3 negocios para reclutar chicas y arreglar visas de EE.UU. para visitar a Jeffrey Epstein, dicen mujeres brasile\u00f1as a la BBC.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Agente Recluta Chicas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Forecasters say storms are becoming more intense in the region, partly due to global warming.\",            \"english_title\": \"Intense Storms Due to Warming\",            \"translated_version\": \"Meteor\u00f3logos dicen que las tormentas se est\u00e1n volviendo m\u00e1s intensas en la regi\u00f3n, en parte por el calentamiento global.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tormentas Intensas por Calentamiento\"        }    ]}"